---
// src/pages/reviews/best-laptops-2026.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Best Laptops 2026 - Buying Guide">
  <article class="review">
    <header class="review-header">
      <span class="category">Laptops</span>
      <h1>Best Laptops 2026: Complete Buying Guide</h1>
      <div class="meta">
        <span>By ReviewCloud</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>March 6, 2026</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="toc">
      <h2>Our Top Picks</h2>
      <p>Looking for the best laptop in 2026? We've tested all the major models to help you find the perfect one.</p>
    </div>

    <section>
      <h2>🍎 Best for Most Users: MacBook Air M4</h2>
      <p>Apple's MacBook Air with M4 chip offers incredible performance at a reasonable price. Perfect for students, professionals, and everyday users.</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> Starting at $999</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>💰 Best Budget: MacBook Neo</h2>
      <p>Apple's most affordable laptop ever at $599. Great for basic tasks and first-time laptop users.</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> Starting at $599</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>🚀 Best Performance: MacBook Pro M5 Max</h2>
      <p>The fastest laptop ever made. Perfect for professionals doing video editing, 3D work, or AI development.</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> Starting at $2,499</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>📱 Best Android: Samsung Galaxy Book</h2>
      <p>Samsung's laptops offer excellent integration with Android phones and great displays.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>How to Choose</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Budget:</strong> $500-800 for basic, $800-1500 for mid-range, $1500+ for pro</li>
        <li><strong>Operating System:</strong> macOS, Windows, or Chrome OS</li>
        <li><strong>Performance:</strong> Consider M4/M5 chips for Apple, latest Intel/AMD for Windows</li>
        <li><strong>Battery Life:</strong> Look for 10+ hours</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <div class="buy-links">
      <h3>Shop Laptops</h3>
      <a href="https://amzn.to/40ypn0N" class="buy-btn" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
        Best Laptop Deals on Amazon
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .review { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; background: white; }
  .review-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .category { background: #667eea; color: white; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.875rem; }
  .review-header h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; margin: 1rem 0; }
  .meta { color: #666; display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; justify-content: center; }
  .toc { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #333; }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin: 0.5rem 0; color: #555; }
  .buy-links { text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; padding: 2rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; }
  .buy-btn { display: inline-block; padding: 1rem 3rem; background: #ff9900; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; }
</style>
